ActSafer Railways Act
SubjectOrder Fixing January 1, 2015 as the Day on which Certain Provisions of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing January 1, 2015 as the day on which sections 10, 12, 43 and 44 and subsection 11(2) of An Act to amend the RAILWAY SAFETY ACT and to make consequential amendments to the Canada Transportation Act and paragraphs 41(2)(g) and 46(g) of the Railway Safety Act COME INTO FORCE.
